THIS. Good god. I think anyone who doesn't think this is horror hasn't been told that their perception of reality is wrong when you know it's not. Hell, it's a major piece of the horror genrewe all know the house is haunted, but the police won't believe you if you tell them that. The idea that the Foundation, in all its credulity toward portals to flesh-temples and parasitic youtube videos and crumbling cities only accessible in dreams and virulently contagious religions and an unkillable adapting lizard, would disbelieve this man? That's horror.







